snippet.title: Leisure Suit Larry - Wet Dreams Don't Dry | Playstation 4 & Nintendo Switch Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Leisure Suit Larry - Wet Dreams Don't Dry is now available on PlayStation 4 & Nintendo Switch!
PlayStation 4: https://bit.ly/2Rfrx0x
Nintendo Switch: https://bit.ly/2XRYdzC

- FOLLOW LARRY LAFFER ON SOCIAL MEDIA -
► Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/LarrysMansion/
► Twitter – https://twitter.com/LarrysMansion
► Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/LarrysMansion/

- ABOUT THE GAME -
Hey ladies, I’m back in business! My new adventure, Leisure Suit Larry - Wet Dreams Don’t Dry, takes me – whatever the route or twist of fate – from the end of the ’80s directly into the 21st century and wow, how the world has changed!
